nodes.text: Protato curls were a lunch side at Dex's Diner on the planet Coruscant prior to the eatery's destruction during the first two years of the Galactic Empire's reign. Made with protatoes, the curly dish was sold for 3.5 credits.
Protato curls were introduced in "Dining at Dex's," a 2009 Hyperspace-exclusive article which was written by Gregory Walker and formatted as an in-universe menu.
